#confirmModal.modal.fade(tabindex='-1', role='dialog', aria-labelledby='myModalLabel', aria-hidden='true')
  .modal-dialog
    .modal-content
      .modal-header
        h2 Are you sure?
      #insideModal.modal-body
       i.fa.fa-warning.fa-4x
       h3 Note: Although KAOS fully endorses trickery and deception, 
        | lying to an admin will result in removal from the game and a healthy showering of foam bullets.
      .modal-footer
       button#confirmAction.btn.btn-default(type='button', data-dismiss='modal') Do it!
       button#cancelAction.btn.btn-default(type='button', data-dismiss='modal') No, nevermind.
